OL,3,CMurderer arrested in Spain after 17
OL,4,Cmonths on the run
OL,6,FA man who stabbed a British person to
OL,7,Fdeath in Portugal has been arrested in
OL,8,FSpain after a "relentless" 17 months
OL,9,Fon the run.
OL,11,FWilliam Hunter, 34, was arrested by
OL,12,FGuardia Civil officers in Alicante on
OL,13,F15 September.
OL,15,FPortuguese authorities will seek to
OL,16,Fextradite him over the border to serve
OL,17,Fa 16-year sentence for murdering his
OL,18,Froommate Elliot Mulligan, 22, in an
OL,19,FAlbufeira apartment in April 2022.
