OL,4,Cmonths on the run
OL,6,FHe was convicted of murder in May
OL,7,F2023, but filed an appeal against the
OL,8,FPortuguese court's judgement.
OL,10,FWhile waiting for the result of the
OL,11,Fappeal, he was released from custody
OL,12,Fon bail in April 2024 following the
OL,13,Fexpiration of his maximum remand
OL,14,Fperiod.
OL,16,FHunter then breached his court-imposed
OL,17,Fbail conditions and fled, sparking the
OL,18,Fmajor multi-agency manhunt that led to
OL,19,Fhis arrest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
