OL,3,CMurderer arrested in Spain after 17
OL,4,Cmonths on the run
OL,6,FHunter's arrest comes after months of
OL,7,Fextensive work between the National
OL,8,FCrime Agency (NCA), Guardia Civil's
OL,9,Ffugitive team, Portuguese Judicial
OL,10,FPolice, and Merseyside Police.
OL,12,FHe remains in custody in Spain while
OL,13,Fhis extradition continues.
OL,15,FThe UK police force has also provided
OL,16,Fongoing support to Elliot Mulligan's
OL,17,Ffamily.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
