OL,6,FNCA Head of Europe Gill Duggan said:
OL,7,F"Above all, our thoughts remain with
OL,8,FElliot's family, who have endured an
OL,9,Funimaginable loss and the painful
OL,10,Freality that the man responsible had
OL,11,Fnot been held accountable for his
OL,12,Fviolent actions.
OL,14,F"Our pursuit of Hunter was relentless,
OL,15,Fdriven by a deep commitment to
OL,16,Fsecuring justice for those who love
OL,17,FElliot.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
