OL,3,CMurderer arrested in Spain after 17
OL,4,Cmonths on the run
OL,6,F"With thanks to our partners at
OL,7,FMerseyside Police and in Spain and
OL,8,FPortugal, Hunter is behind bars where
OL,9,Fhe belongs, and where he will remain
OL,10,Ffor a long time to come."
OL,12,FMerseyside Police Detective
OL,13,FSuperintendent Mark Drew said: "The
OL,14,Farrest of William Hunter was part of a
OL,15,Fjoint operation between Merseyside
OL,16,FPolice, NCA, Guardia Civil's fugitive
OL,17,Fteam and Portuguese Judicial Police.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
