OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F393A1758826433
OL,3,CMurderer arrested in Spain after 17
OL,4,Cmonths on the run
OL,6,F"We are committed to working with our
OL,7,Fpartners to capture those that evade
OL,8,Flaw enforcement and bring them to
OL,9,Fjustice.
OL,11,F"We will continue to support Elliot's
OL,12,Ffamily, as they finally see justice
OL,13,Fbeing done after their tragic loss, we
OL,14,Fhope that the arrest of William Hunter
OL,15,Fbrings them some comfort.
